    "We argue that this level of expertise is crucial when evaluating LLM outputs, as LLMs may lack the ability to fully capture the complexity involved in complex tasks.",
    "In addition, while lay persons may possess critical thinking skills, they lack the depth of understanding required to make clinical judgements accurately [57].",
    "An average LLM user may not recognize inaccuracies or the importance of certain dietary restrictions and mental health protocols and is less likely to be aware of the latest research and clinical guidelines.",
    "Dataset CurationWe crafted a dataset of 25 instructions for both the dietetics and mental health domains to test the evaluations performed by both the LLM and the SMEs.",
    "This dataset was designed to provide a diverse range of instructions and questions that would challenge both the ability of the LLM to provide accurate and complex responses and the clinical judgment of the SME."
